ansmission eigenvalues\ndetermines the probability distributions of intensity and total transmission\nfor a single incident channel.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Mar 2013 18:37:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 17 Feb 2014 04:46:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-02-18"}
