fortable suggestion\nof a factor of 3 to 5 growth in size for the compact, z ~ 1.5 galaxies that are\nknown to possess infant disks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Mar 2013 08:27:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-15"}
